                    <mo>&#xB7;</mo>
                    <mi>V</mi>
                    <mo>=</mo>
                    <mn>180</mn>
                    <mo>&#xB7;</mo>
                    <mn>0</mn>
                    <mo>.</mo>
                    <mn>5</mn>
                    <mo>=</mo>
                    <mn>90</mn>
                    <mi>W</mi>
                </math>
            </equation>
            <para>With 4 propulsion engines, each engine must have a power of <emphasis role="bold"
                    >22.5W≅25W</emphasis> per engine.<footnote>
                    <para>with the assumption that the motors and their controls have an efficiency
                        close to 100%.</para>
                </footnote></para>
